title: Match of the Day - 7th March 2015 - hdtv x264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD     
Date: Saturday 7th March 2015 
Time: 22:45 to 23:15 

Jacqui Oatley introduces highlights of the Premier League game between QPR and Tottenham at Loftus Road, introduced by Steve Bower. Spurs have won only once in six visits to Loftus Road during the Premier League era. However, they beat their relegation-threatened London neighbours 4-0 at White Hart Lane earlier in the season.
There's a separate Match of the Day show for the FA Cup highlights.
